  "texts": [
    "We categorize these detection tasks based on the specific requirements of traffic scenarios, allowing readers to quickly locate the sections that interest them and gain in-depth insights into relevant information.3) Regarding the optimization of object detection algorithms, we systematically review optimization methods for object detection techniques in traffic scenarios.",
    "This encompasses four aspects: feature enhancement, context-based information, super-resolution techniques, and loss functions.",
    "These insights are intended to assist researchers in improving detection performance across various traffic scenarios.",
    "4)We analyze and summarize the applications of 16 datasets in different traffic scenarios, providing detailed information about these datasets.",
    "This information aids researchers in selecting datasets that align with their research objectives and evaluating their algorithm's performance effectively.Through these contributions, our research aims to provide comprehensive references and guidance for object detection research in traffic scenarios, thereby fostering the Development and advancement of this field.These contributions collectively provide the most up-to-date, thorough, and comprehensive survey, distinctively different from previous review works."
